{"cells": [{"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["# Hướng Dẫn Chạy Nhanh (Sử dụng Cell ID) (By Cell Number)\n", "# Hướng Dẫn Chạy Nhanh (Sử dụng Cell ID) (By Cell Number)\n", "# Hướng Dẫn Chạy Nhanh (Sử dụng Cell ID) (By Cell Number)\n", "# Hướng Dẫn Chạy Nhanh (Sử dụng Cell ID) (By Cell Number)\n", "# Hướng Dẫn Chạy Nhanh (Sử dụng Cell ID) (By Cell Number)\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "## Mode A - Run API nhanh (khong train lai, da co checkpoint)\n", "## Mode A - Run API nhanh (khong train lai, da co checkpoint)\n", "## Mode A - Run API nhanh (khong train lai, da co checkpoint)\n", "## Mode A - Run API nhanh (khong train lai, da co checkpoint)\n", "## Mode A - Run API nhanh (khong train lai, da co checkpoint)\n", "Chay theo thu tu: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Chay theo thu tu: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Chay theo thu tu: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Chay theo thu tu: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Chay theo thu tu: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib`\n", "- Da co `/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib`\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "## Mode B - Neu thieu `best_xgb.joblib` (can train lai XGBoost)\n", "## Mode B - Neu thieu `best_xgb.joblib` (can train lai XGBoost)\n", "## Mode B - Neu thieu `best_xgb.joblib` (can train lai XGBoost)\n", "## Mode B - Neu thieu `best_xgb.joblib` (can train lai XGBoost)\n", "## Mode B - Neu thieu `best_xgb.joblib` (can train lai XGBoost)\n", "Tao lai XGBoost checkpoint: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19**\n", "Tao lai XGBoost checkpoint: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19**\n", "Tao lai XGBoost checkpoint: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19**\n", "Tao lai XGBoost checkpoint: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19**\n", "Tao lai XGBoost checkpoint: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19**\n", "Sau do chay API: **30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Sau do chay API: **30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Sau do chay API: **30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Sau do chay API: **30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "Sau do chay API: **30 → 31 → 33 → 34**\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "Dieu kien:\n", "- Da co `phobert_finetuned_best.pt` (Cell 13 se load best checkpoint tu dieu nay)\n", "- Da co `phobert_finetuned_best.pt` (Cell 13 se load best checkpoint tu dieu nay)\n", "- Da co `phobert_finetuned_best.pt` (Cell 13 se load best checkpoint tu dieu nay)\n", "- Da co `phobert_finetuned_best.pt` (Cell 13 se load best checkpoint tu dieu nay)\n", "- Da co `phobert_finetuned_best.pt` (Cell 13 se load best checkpoint tu dieu nay)\n", "- Chua co `best_xgb.joblib` (Cell 19 se tao va luu file nay)\n", "- Chua co `best_xgb.joblib` (Cell 19 se tao va luu file nay)\n", "- Chua co `best_xgb.joblib` (Cell 19 se tao va luu file nay)\n", "- Chua co `best_xgb.joblib` (Cell 19 se tao va luu file nay)\n", "- Chua co `best_xgb.joblib` (Cell 19 se tao va luu file nay)\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "## Mode C - Train full + danh gia (lan dau chay, chua co gi)\n", "## Mode C - Train full + danh gia (lan dau chay, chua co gi)\n", "## Mode C - Train full + danh gia (lan dau chay, chua co gi)\n", "## Mode C - Train full + danh gia (lan dau chay, chua co gi)\n", "## Mode C - Train full + danh gia (lan dau chay, chua co gi)\n", "Chay: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19 → 21 → 23 → 24 → 25 → 26 → 28**\n", "Chay: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19 → 21 → 23 → 24 → 25 → 26 → 28**\n", "Chay: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19 → 21 → 23 → 24 → 25 → 26 → 28**\n", "Chay: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19 → 21 → 23 → 24 → 25 → 26 → 28**\n", "Chay: **4 → 5 → 7 → 9 → 11 → 12 → 13 → 15 → 16 → 18 → 19 → 21 → 23 → 24 → 25 → 26 → 28**\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "## Smoke test sau khi bat API (Cell 34)\n", "## Smoke test sau khi bat API (Cell 34)\n", "## Smoke test sau khi bat API (Cell 34)\n", "## Smoke test sau khi bat API (Cell 34)\n", "## Smoke test sau khi bat API (Cell 34)\n", "- `GET /health` phai co `\"ready\": true`\n", "- `GET /health` phai co `\"ready\": true`\n", "- `GET /health` phai co `\"ready\": true`\n", "- `GET /health` phai co `\"ready\": true`\n", "- `GET /health` phai co `\"ready\": true`\n", "- `POST /predict` 2 cau khac nhau phai ra xac suat khac nhau (khong phai luc nao cung 0.5)", "- `POST /predict` 2 cau khac nhau phai ra xac suat khac nhau (khong phai luc nao cung 0.5)", "- `POST /predict` 2 cau khac nhau phai ra xac suat khac nhau (khong phai luc nao cung 0.5)", "- `POST /predict` 2 cau khac nhau phai ra xac suat khac nhau (khong phai luc nao cung 0.5)", "- `POST /predict` 2 cau khac nhau phai ra xac suat khac nhau (khong phai luc nao cung 0.5)"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "1olNtKppwTAu"}, "source": ["# 🧪 Thực Nghiệm: Kết Hợp PhoBERT Fine-tuned và XGBoost: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)\n", "# 🧪 Thực Nghiệm: Kết Hợp PhoBERT Fine-tuned và XGBoost: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)\n", "# 🧪 Thực Nghiệm: Kết Hợp PhoBERT Fine-tuned và XGBoost: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)\n", "# 🧪 Thực Nghiệm: Kết Hợp PhoBERT Fine-tuned và XGBoost: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)\n", "# 🧪 Thực Nghiệm: Kết Hợp PhoBERT Fine-tuned và XGBoost: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)\n", "## Phát hiện đánh giá giả mạo trên sàn TMĐT Việt Nam\n", "## Phát hiện đánh giá giả mạo trên sàn TMĐT Việt Nam\n", "## Phát hiện đánh giá giả mạo trên sàn TMĐT Việt Nam\n", "## Phát hiện đánh giá giả mạo trên sàn TMĐT Việt Nam\n", "## Phát hiện đánh giá giả mạo trên sàn TMĐT Việt Nam\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "**Mục tiêu:** Thử nghiệm phương pháp Enstôible:\n", "**Mục tiêu:** Thử nghiệm phương pháp Enstôible:\n", "**Mục tiêu:** Thử nghiệm phương pháp Enstôible:\n", "**Mục tiêu:** Thử nghiệm phương pháp Enstôible:\n", "**Mục tiêu:** Thử nghiệm phương pháp Enstôible:\n", "1. Fine-tune PhoBERT → trích xuất tôibedding task-specific\n", "1. Fine-tune PhoBERT → trích xuất tôibedding task-specific\n", "1. Fine-tune PhoBERT → trích xuất tôibedding task-specific\n", "1. Fine-tune PhoBERT → trích xuất tôibedding task-specific\n", "1. Fine-tune PhoBERT → trích xuất tôibedding task-specific\n", "2. Kết hợp tôibedding fine-tuned + handcrafted features\n", "2. Kết hợp tôibedding fine-tuned + handcrafted features\n", "2. Kết hợp tôibedding fine-tuned + handcrafted features\n", "2. Kết hợp tôibedding fine-tuned + handcrafted features\n", "2. Kết hợp tôibedding fine-tuned + handcrafted features\n", "3. Huấn luyện XGBoost trên combined features\n", "3. Huấn luyện XGBoost trên combined features\n", "3. Huấn luyện XGBoost trên combined features\n", "3. Huấn luyện XGBoost trên combined features\n", "3. Huấn luyện XGBoost trên combined features\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "\n", "**So sánh với:**\n", "**So sánh với:**\n", "**So sánh với:**\n", "**So sánh với:**\n", "**So sánh với:**\n", "- XGBoost + Combined (frozen PhoBERT): 87.64%\n", "- XGBoost + Combined (frozen PhoBERT): 87.64%\n", "- XGBoost + Combined (frozen PhoBERT): 87.64%\n", "- XGBoost + Combined (frozen PhoBERT): 87.64%\n", "- XGBoost + Combined (frozen PhoBERT): 87.64%\n", "- PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): 90.92%", "- PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): 90.92%", "- PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): 90.92%", "- PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): 90.92%", "- PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): 90.92%"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "OKLXMt9AwTAv"}, "source": ["## 1. Setup & Install", "## 1. Setup & Install", "## 1. Setup & Install", "## 1. Setup & Install", "## 1. Setup & Install"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 2, "metadata": {"id": "7HvryqgRwTAw"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["\u001b[2K   \u001b[90m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m \u001b[32m413.9/413.9 kB\u001b[0m \u001b[31m16.0 MB/s\u001b[0m eta \u001b[36m0:00:00\u001b[0m\n", "\u001b[?25h"]}], "source": ["!pip install -q fastapi uvicorn pyngrok transformers xgboost torch joblib optuna psutil seaborn scikit-learn"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 3, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"}, "id": "8DWSPUl3wTAw", "outputId": "f56529e4-f1cc-4eba-d595-6db569d8ae65"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["🖥️ Colab FREE | Device: cpu\n"]}], "source": ["import os, gc, json, time, warnings\n", "import numpy as np\n", "import pandas as pd\n", "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n", "import seaborn as sns\n", "import torch\n", "import torch.nn as nn\n", "from torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader\n", "from transformers import AutoTokenizer, AutoModel, get_linear_schedule_with_warmup\n", "from sklearn.metrics import (\n", "    accuracy_score, precision_score, recall_score, f1_score,\n", "    classification_report, confusion_matrix, roc_auc_score, roc_curve\n", ")\n", "import xgboost as xgb\n", "import optuna\n", "import psutil\n", "\n", "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n", "optuna.logging.set_verbosity(optuna.logging.WARNING)\n", "\n", "device = torch.device('cuda' if torch.cuda.is_available() else 'cpu')\n", "total_ram = psutil.virtual_mtôiory().total / (1024**3)\n", "COLAB_TIER = 'PRO' if total_ram > 30 else 'FREE'\n", "\n", "print(f'🖥️ Colab {COLAB_TIER} | Device: {device}')\n", "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n", "    print(f'   GPU: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}')\n", "    print(f'   VRAM: {torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_mtôiory / (1024**3):.1f} GB')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "c1ydUlZywTAx"}, "source": ["## 2. Load Data & Config", "## 2. Load Data & Config", "## 2. Load Data & Config", "## 2. Load Data & Config", "## 2. Load Data & Config"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 4, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"}, "id": "Et37n7n6wTAx", "outputId": "2f4c8c89-8ea6-42b4-82dc-02995b20fdfd"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Mounted at /content/drive\n", "✅ Data loaded: train=14306, dev=1590, test=3974\n", "📋 Config: BS_FT=16, Epochs=3, Trials=60\n"]}], "source": ["from google.colab import drive\n", "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n", "\n", "DRIVE_PATH = '/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection'\n", "DATA_PATH = f'{DRIVE_PATH}/data'\n", "RESULT_PATH = f'{DRIVE_PATH}/results'\n", "MODEL_PATH = f'{DRIVE_PATH}/models'\n", "os.makedirs(RESULT_PATH, exist_ok=True)\n", "os.makedirs(MODEL_PATH, exist_ok=True)\n", "\n", "# Load data\n", "df_train = pd.read_csv(f'{DATA_PATH}/train.csv')\n", "df_dev = pd.read_csv(f'{DATA_PATH}/dev.csv')\n", "df_test = pd.read_csv(f'{DATA_PATH}/test.csv')\n", "\n", "y_train = df_train['Label'].values\n", "y_dev = df_dev['Label'].values\n", "y_test = df_test['Label'].values\n", "\n", "train_texts = df_train['Comment'].fillna('').tolist()\n", "dev_texts = df_dev['Comment'].fillna('').tolist()\n", "test_texts = df_test['Comment'].fillna('').tolist()\n", "\n", "# Config theo tier\n", "MAX_LEN = 128\n", "BATCH_SIZE_FT = 16 if COLAB_TIER == 'FREE' else 32\n", "BATCH_SIZE_EXTRACT = 32 if COLAB_TIER == 'FREE' else 64\n", "NUM_EPOCHS_FT = 3 if COLAB_TIER == 'FREE' else 5\n", "LR_FT = 2e-5\n", "OPTUNA_TRIALS = 60 if COLAB_TIER == 'FREE' else 120\n", "PHOBERT_MODEL = 'vinai/phobert-base'\n", "EMBED_DIM = 768\n", "\n", "print(f'✅ Data loaded: train={len(y_train)}, dev={len(y_dev)}, test={len(y_test)}')\n", "print(f'📋 Config: BS_FT={BATCH_SIZE_FT}, Epochs={NUM_EPOCHS_FT}, Trials={OPTUNA_TRIALS}')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "ZfACizuZwTAx"}, "source": ["## 3. Handcrafted Feature Extraction\n", "## 3. Handcrafted Feature Extraction\n", "## 3. Handcrafted Feature Extraction\n", "## 3. Handcrafted Feature Extraction\n", "## 3. Handcrafted Feature Extraction\n", "Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công (giống notebook 03)", "Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công (giống notebook 03)", "Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công (giống notebook 03)", "Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công (giống notebook 03)", "Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công (giống notebook 03)"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 5, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"}, "id": "EDNYh3tZwTAx", "outputId": "e0421a1e-16bc-41c3-8e0d-321d53b8f7ee"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["📊 Trích xuất handcrafted features...\n", "✅ Handcrafted features: 12 features\n"]}], "source": ["import re\n", "\n", "def extract_handcrafted_features(text):\n", "    \"\"\"Trích xuất 12 đặc trưng thủ công từ text.\"\"\"\n", "    if not isinstance(text, str) or len(text.strip()) == 0:\n", "        return np.zeros(12)\n", "\n", "    words = text.split()\n", "    n_words = max(len(words), 1)\n", "    n_chars = max(len(text), 1)\n", "\n", "    features = [\n", "        len(text),                                          # 1. Độ dài text\n", "        n_words,                                            # 2. Số từ\n", "        n_chars / n_words,                                  # 3. Độ dài trung bình từ\n", "        sum(1 for c in text if c.isupper()) / n_chars,      # 4. Tỷ lệ chữ hoa\n", "        text.count('!'),                                    # 5. Số dấu chấm than\n", "        text.count('?'),                                    # 6. Số dấu hỏi\n", "        len(re.findall(r'[😀-🙏🌀-🗿🚀-🛿✂-➰]', text)),  # 7. Số tôioji\n", "        1 if n_words <= 5 else 0,                           # 8. Review ngắn (<=5 từ)\n", "        1 if n_words >= 100 else 0,                         # 9. Review dài (>=100 từ)\n", "        sum(1 for c in text if c.isdigit()) / n_chars,      # 10. Tỷ lệ số\n", "        len(set(words)) / n_words,                          # 11. Tỷ lệ từ unique\n", "        text.count('\\n'),                                   # 12. Số dòng mới\n", "    ]\n", "    return np.array(features, dtype=np.float32)\n", "\n", "# Trích xuất cho tất cả các tập\n", "print('📊 Trích xuất handcrafted features...')\n", "X_hc_train = np.array([extract_handcrafted_features(t) for t in train_texts])\n", "X_hc_dev = np.array([extract_handcrafted_features(t) for t in dev_texts])\n", "X_hc_test = np.array([extract_handcrafted_features(t) for t in test_texts])\n", "print(f'✅ Handcrafted features: {X_hc_train.shape[1]} features')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "Iup73iJ6wTAy"}, "source": ["## 4. PHASE 1: Fine-tune PhoBERT\n", "## 4. PHASE 1: Fine-tune PhoBERT\n", "## 4. PHASE 1: Fine-tune PhoBERT\n", "## 4. PHASE 1: Fine-tune PhoBERT\n", "## 4. PHASE 1: Fine-tune PhoBERT\n", "Fine-tune PhoBERT trên bài toán spam detection trước, rồi dùng mô hình đã fine-tune để trích xuất tôibedding.", "Fine-tune PhoBERT trên bài toán spam detection trước, rồi dùng mô hình đã fine-tune để trích xuất tôibedding.", "Fine-tune PhoBERT trên bài toán spam detection trước, rồi dùng mô hình đã fine-tune để trích xuất tôibedding.", "Fine-tune PhoBERT trên bài toán spam detection trước, rồi dùng mô hình đã fine-tune để trích xuất tôibedding.", "Fine-tune PhoBERT trên bài toán spam detection trước, rồi dùng mô hình đã fine-tune để trích xuất tôibedding."]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 11, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 217, "referenced_widgets": ["53be4a32e81e404aae366967cd2af521", "305b5eec5c7541b1a33a40b286d39517", "99cbfba5b9d943f19acc7fb458b29c66", "d80e2c83498747fabe9a40f830b61751", "99654dd3e7294c7295fba1ff8a16b2b9", "91629157a34046a69cea7532287b7aa7", "45485a7e881e4b7f91f47f9945aa4340", "f17614108b3943aa940334b289f0436e", "462be3dfd1044c3ba0eb58bf6c4b0c1a", "30a1a268af104a1dabb08df3c828c1b4", "39888741021c43a487862f1f192c4e0a", "db8b2bda56254335a733ea6c8e639ed9", "41a1288b9c3e445194dbbbbf34dcd334", "93332e82ca8c4d698ddf734c5b7af438", "e9a1a4d535564d3491f35db849a77411", "3d1d7daac794499f83d6ab84c17c8923", "7a3b5fd47db44d35b83dbf12a4893bb3", "796bf4bd875e4bb6bdaae439b56456c8", "402a9b3c70474d0699dd5832029c3d8b", "1c0768a844ef40b087952a303eb7a475", "459a146de13841b48607d7d5c56c69b4", "6d3823f4b9bb4654bf24f5b65149d8c0", "6ce82702672a4fdd8c1f973e66eacaf1", "c53eca98adee438aa81170e6f1440e50", "c92f6adac6ea43c1b728061b543adee3", "a8331832ba534fef88fef955fcc3afea", "227b900f87174d83a760853c2919b678", "b4624d1253b8457e9317262790e5de32", "2cc5141881324665a816e7f18d0b9cfe", "33a34467d2bf4da8bcdec4d459547aba", "885e761f62cc4a99abb942a5a6fd325c", "f73c5b11d702456f80f272d38746bd6d", "1fada0fdca1a4202a5c29da246c1e405", "ba7ef333be744a5b9e69a0d90f5a3a90", "036978bf876941ef977a2582a775e301", "3fecc873f1d84138bde930119a9fba81", "c202830c5ba04ff58c8a9966f320d6c4", "4ec274220a1248db9b218510f97a7b9b", "55d03aaa879048478972d969cd09dd0c", "909e660121a84fdab61aa723d7ae43eb", "93764ce25f9a479aa1151c5b284a89ef", "f9773ac2f2a945faa57100fe272afbde", "0d3bf95bced541a69d400c846f6e1265", "b25e459097514dacac2de83457641bc4"]}, "id": "1yVeSDgdwTAy", "outputId": "23891e9c-8a0e-467f-ed8b-b962212e591d"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stderr", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Warning: You are sending unauthenticated requests to the HF Hub. Please set a HF_TOKEN to enable higher rate limits and faster downloads.\n", "WARNING:huggingface_hub.utils._http:Warning: You are sending unauthenticated requests to the HF Hub. Please set a HF_TOKEN to enable higher rate limits and faster downloads.\n"]}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "448a310e3af448a7829ac8b404041db4", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["config.json:   0%|          | 0.00/557 [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "8ccc19014bf74159a8fb7f06e99aed51", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["vocab.txt: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "d7655c0a00034bb8a806ab93fbebf540", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["bpe.codes: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "893f76eaed26477d9d36f27f8a36f127", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["tokenizer.json: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["✅ Datasets ready: train=14306, dev=1590, test=3974\n"]}], "source": ["# Load tokenizer\n", "tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(PHOBERT_MODEL)\n", "\n", "class SpamDataset(Dataset):\n", "    \"\"\"Dataset cho PhoBERT fine-tuning.\"\"\"\n", "    def __init__(self, texts, labels, tokenizer, max_len=256):\n", "        self.texts = texts\n", "        self.labels = labels\n", "        self.tokenizer = tokenizer\n", "        self.max_len = max_len\n", "\n", "    def __len__(self):\n", "        return len(self.texts)\n", "\n", "    def __getittôi__(self, idx):\n", "        encoding = self.tokenizer(\n", "            self.texts[idx],\n", "            max_length=self.max_len,\n", "            padding='max_length',\n", "            truncation=True,\n", "            return_tensors='pt'\n", "        )\n", "        return {\n", "            'input_ids': encoding['input_ids'].squeeze(),\n", "            'attention_mask': encoding['attention_mask'].squeeze(),\n", "            'label': torch.tensor(self.labels[idx], dtype=torch.long)\n", "        }\n", "\n", "# Tạo datasets\n", "train_dataset = SpamDataset(train_texts, y_train, tokenizer, MAX_LEN)\n", "dev_dataset = SpamDataset(dev_texts, y_dev, tokenizer, MAX_LEN)\n", "test_dataset = SpamDataset(test_texts, y_test, tokenizer, MAX_LEN)\n", "\n", "train_loader = DataLoader(train_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_FT, shuffle=True)\n", "dev_loader = DataLoader(dev_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_FT)\n", "test_loader = DataLoader(test_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_FT)\n", "\n", "print(f'✅ Datasets ready: train={len(train_dataset)}, dev={len(dev_dataset)}, test={len(test_dataset)}')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 12, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 373, "referenced_widgets": ["c95fb098fc724c1d9337009417e43d2a", "ed55ddd30304430ba89202a6ed7c0ab5", "aa42446336bc4554bb0451103b455da4", "418b5a56e4b64d2f9bec09e1b348efcd", "92dd041665554228bbb15a1ef3071d75", "4263afba74df4473b6c5b4e14cc48843", "cb6bfefd79944f0fa0a9e1eb590d62c6", "000facfec70e4080903da1a798d7207e", "707ad56a2e23494aa8b45a1da51269cf", "eb202c0c942a419bb8e067efabd4d69f", "356d2e59e71b40d3b2551bbed1ab8b5b", "2f846fb30c8f4c618ddb833c41b175fa", "4f6b9472955e4e799ca0ac4b1a8520f7", "010312ede7b1425f95a07df717117e73", "eb58c9a88ddf4c8892127830ecaa4bfb", "7594b37ccd184ce1bd67d7be19e7b261", "22a6a35dc149409383d9d1f3994ee4b0", "62c8d32f8ab5426a85242f1a251de5d5", "624fe29edac84276b72ea2bd389c41c6", "886518ed55c64c4da5fa350da79891f3", "131238fde34d43c09909d655744352e9", "0335728790f448cbbbdd2d5d1c18cb0b", "3c330c261a354c589a90dd8ed5899f26", "ad1aef8f63f444a1b0e19a54cc3b96da", "ead9bc5f321048a2ad9223a98261543c", "660bd8608b2546c6afff2d8dc3b17efa", "d901715031e44c5eabe4d6385a75310e", "fd3296e90f2d42f8afac2061ce512d1c", "31625489740042bdb374c728a428c741", "8a567d3f3e3140b1ba589c59eb908a56", "9e67795db83740feb9eedb64d4bbee93", "538194b5b87a48c083aa1969590f9aba", "323aafa7648147e98b422b69fa8e5a71"]}, "id": "3V41LvafwTAy", "outputId": "358fb191-9698-44f6-8630-e15ba6c8294a"}, "outputs": [{"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "4e3f9f5f6bc342bb9d1e6fe51934a3c8", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["pytorch_model.bin:   0%|          | 0.00/543M [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "9188e033c9014ce8874cf131b947f58e", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["Loading weights:   0%|          | 0/199 [00:00<?, ?it/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "63c52b5008704d8781da1be456b70dc5", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["model.safetensors:   0%|          | 0.00/543M [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stderr", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["RobertaModel LOAD REPORT from: vinai/phobert-base\n", "Key                             | Status     |  | \n", "--------------------------------+------------+--+-\n", "lm_head.dense.bias              | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "roberta.embeddings.position_ids | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.decoder.weight          | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.dense.weight            | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.decoder.bias            | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.layer_norm.bias         | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.layer_norm.weight       | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "lm_head.bias                    | UNEXPECTED |  | \n", "\n", "Notes:\n", "- UNEXPECTED\t:can be ignored when loading from different task/architecture; not ok if you expect identical arch.\n"]}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["✅ Model loaded: 134,999,810 parameters\n"]}], "source": ["class PhoBERTClassifier(nn.Module):\n", "    \"\"\"PhoBERT + Classification Head.\"\"\"\n", "    def __init__(self, model_name, num_classes=2, dropout=0.1):\n", "        super().__init__()\n", "        self.phobert = AutoModel.from_pretrained(model_name)\n", "        self.dropout = nn.Dropout(dropout)\n", "        self.classifier = nn.Linear(self.phobert.config.hidden_size, num_classes)\n", "\n", "    def forward(self, input_ids, attention_mask=None):\n", "        outputs = self.phobert(input_ids=input_ids, attention_mask=attention_mask)\n", "        cls_output = outputs.last_hidden_state[:, 0, :]  # [CLS] token\n", "        cls_output = self.dropout(cls_output)\n", "        logits = self.classifier(cls_output)\n", "        return logits\n", "\n", "    def extract_tôibeddings(self, input_ids, attention_mask=None):\n", "        \"\"\"Trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] từ PhoBERT đã fine-tuned (không qua classifier).\"\"\"\n", "        with torch.no_grad():\n", "            outputs = self.phobert(input_ids=input_ids, attention_mask=attention_mask)\n", "            cls_output = outputs.last_hidden_state[:, 0, :]  # [CLS] token, 768-dim\n", "        return cls_output\n", "\n", "# Khởi tạo model\n", "model = PhoBERTClassifier(PHOBERT_MODEL).to(device)\n", "print(f'✅ Model loaded: {sum(p.numel() for p in model.parameters()):,} parameters')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 13, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 530}, "id": "r344ZthmwTAy", "outputId": "4abb986d-326d-43f1-8797-0496e653273c"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["🚀 GPU detected: Tesla T4\n", "✅ Mixed Precision (FP16) enabled for 2x-3x speedup.\n", "============================================================\n", "🚀 PHASE 1: Fine-tuning PhoBERT (Optimized Version)\n", "============================================================\n", "📋 Config: 3 epochs, 895 batches/epoch, MAX_LEN=128\n", "\n", "--- Epoch 1/3 ---\n", "  🏋️ Train: [██████████████████████████████] 100.0% | Loss: 0.4027 | 6.9 b/s | ETA: 0.0sss\n", "  ✅ Train done | Loss: 0.4027 | ⏱️ 2m 9s\n", "  📊 Dev F1: 0.8074 | Acc: 0.8289 | ⏱️ Epoch: 2m 12s\n", "  ⏱️ Elapsed: 2m 12s | Est. Remaining: 4m 24s\n", "  💾 Saved Best Model (F1: 0.8074)\n", "\n", "--- Epoch 2/3 ---\n", "  🏋️ Train: [██████████████████████████████] 100.0% | Loss: 0.2648 | 6.7 b/s | ETA: 0.0sss\n", "  ✅ Train done | Loss: 0.2648 | ⏱️ 2m 13s\n", "  📊 Dev F1: 0.8700 | Acc: 0.8937 | ⏱️ Epoch: 2m 16s\n", "  ⏱️ Elapsed: 4m 33s | Est. Remaining: 2m 16s\n", "  💾 Saved Best Model (F1: 0.8700)\n", "\n", "--- Epoch 3/3 ---\n", "  🏋️ Train: [██████████████████████████████] 100.0% | Loss: 0.1998 | 6.6 b/s | ETA: 0.0sss\n", "  ✅ Train done | Loss: 0.1998 | ⏱️ 2m 14s\n", "  📊 Dev F1: 0.8808 | Acc: 0.9069 | ⏱️ Epoch: 2m 17s\n", "  ⏱️ Elapsed: 6m 53s | Est. Remaining: 0.0s\n", "  💾 Saved Best Model (F1: 0.8808)\n", "\n", "✅ Fine-tuning complete! Best Dev F1: 0.8808 | Total Time: 6m 58s\n", "CPU times: user 6min 38s, sys: 2.55 s, total: 6min 41s\n", "Wall time: 6min 58s\n"]}], "source": ["%%time\n", "# === FINE-TUNING OPTIMIZED ===\n", "import time, sys\n", "from datetime import timedelta\n", "import torch.cuda.amp as amp # Mixed Precision\n", "\n", "# GPU Check\n", "if device.type == 'cpu':\n", "    print('❌ CRITICAL WARNING: Running on CPU will take ~10+ hours!')\n", "    print('👉 Please go to Runtime > Change runtime type > Select T4 GPU.')\n", "    # sys.exit('GPU not found. Stopping to save time.') # Optional: hard stop\n", "else:\n", "    print(f'🚀 GPU detected: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}')\n", "    print('✅ Mixed Precision (FP16) enabled for 2x-3x speedup.')\n", "\n", "def format_time(seconds):\n", "    if seconds < 60: return f'{seconds:.1f}s'\n", "    m, s = divmod(int(seconds), 60)\n", "    if m < 60: return f'{m}m {s}s'\n", "    h, m = divmod(m, 60)\n", "    return f'{h}h {m}m {s}s'\n", "\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print('🚀 PHASE 1: Fine-tuning PhoBERT (Optimized Version)')\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print(f'📋 Config: {NUM_EPOCHS_FT} epochs, {len(train_loader)} batches/epoch, MAX_LEN={MAX_LEN}')\n", "\n", "optimizer = torch.optim.AdamW(model.parameters(), lr=LR_FT, weight_decay=0.01)\n", "total_steps = len(train_loader) * NUM_EPOCHS_FT\n", "scheduler = get_linear_schedule_with_warmup(optimizer, int(0.1*total_steps), total_steps)\n", "scaler = amp.GradScaler() # FP16 Scaler\n", "\n", "n_real, n_spam = (y_train == 0).sum(), (y_train == 1).sum()\n", "class_weights = torch.tensor([1.0, n_real / n_spam], dtype=torch.float).to(device)\n", "criterion = nn.CrossEntropyLoss(weight=class_weights)\n", "\n", "best_f1, patience, no_improve = 0, 2, 0\n", "epoch_times, phase_start = [], time.time()\n", "\n", "for epoch in range(NUM_EPOCHS_FT):\n", "    epoch_start = time.time()\n", "    print(f'\\n--- Epoch {epoch+1}/{NUM_EPOCHS_FT} ---')\n", "\n", "    # --- TRAIN ---\n", "    model.train()\n", "    total_loss, num_batches = 0, len(train_loader)\n", "    train_start = time.time()\n", "\n", "    for batch_idx, batch in enumerate(train_loader):\n", "        inputs, masks, labels = batch['input_ids'].to(device), batch['attention_mask'].to(device), batch['label'].to(device)\n", "\n", "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n", "        with amp.autocast(): # Mixed Precision Context\n", "            logits = model(inputs, masks)\n", "            loss = criterion(logits, labels)\n", "\n", "        scaler.scale(loss).backward()\n", "        scaler.unscale_(optimizer)\n", "        torch.nn.utils.clip_grad_norm_(model.parameters(), 1.0)\n", "        scaler.step(optimizer)\n", "        scaler.update()\n", "        scheduler.step()\n", "        total_loss += loss.ittôi()\n", "\n", "        if (batch_idx + 1) % 10 == 0 or (batch_idx + 1) == num_batches:\n", "            elapsed = time.time() - train_start\n", "            speed = (batch_idx + 1) / elapsed\n", "            eta = (num_batches - (batch_idx + 1)) / speed\n", "            bar = '█' * int(30 * (batch_idx+1)/num_batches) + '░' * (30 - int(30 * (batch_idx+1)/num_batches))\n", "            print(f'\\r  🏋️ Train: [{bar}] {(batch_idx+1)/num_batches*100:5.1f}% | Loss: {total_loss/(batch_idx+1):.4f} | {speed:.1f} b/s | ETA: {format_time(eta)}', end='', flush=True)\n", "\n", "    train_time = time.time() - train_start\n", "    print(f'\\n  ✅ Train done | Loss: {total_loss/num_batches:.4f} | ⏱️ {format_time(train_time)}')\n", "\n", "    # --- EVAL ---\n", "    model.eval()\n", "    dev_preds, eval_start = [], time.time()\n", "    with torch.no_grad(), amp.autocast():\n", "        for batch in dev_loader:\n", "            logits = model(batch['input_ids'].to(device), batch['attention_mask'].to(device))\n", "            dev_preds.extend(logits.argmax(dim=-1).cpu().numpy())\n", "\n", "    dev_f1 = f1_score(y_dev, dev_preds, average='macro')\n", "    epoch_time = time.time() - epoch_start\n", "    epoch_times.append(epoch_time)\n", "\n", "    print(f'  📊 Dev F1: {dev_f1:.4f} | Acc: {accuracy_score(y_dev, dev_preds):.4f} | ⏱️ Epoch: {format_time(epoch_time)}')\n", "    print(f'  ⏱️ Elapsed: {format_time(time.time()-phase_start)} | Est. Rtôiaining: {format_time(epoch_time * (NUM_EPOCHS_FT - epoch - 1))}')\n", "\n", "    if dev_f1 > best_f1:\n", "        best_f1 = dev_f1\n", "        no_improve = 0\n", "        torch.save(model.state_dict(), f'{MODEL_PATH}/phobert_finetuned_best.pt')\n", "        print(f'  💾 Saved Best Model (F1: {best_f1:.4f})')\n", "    else:\n", "        no_improve += 1\n", "        if no_improve >= patience:\n", "            print(f'  ⏹️ Early stopping at epoch {epoch+1}')\n", "            break\n", "\n", "model.load_state_dict(torch.load(f'{MODEL_PATH}/phobert_finetuned_best.pt'))\n", "print(f'\\n✅ Fine-tuning complete! Best Dev F1: {best_f1:.4f} | Total Time: {format_time(time.time()-phase_start)}')\n"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "t2s-BxHRwTAz"}, "source": ["## 5. PHASE 2: Trích xuất Embedding từ PhoBERT đã Fine-tuned\n", "## 5. PHASE 2: Trích xuất Embedding từ PhoBERT đã Fine-tuned\n", "## 5. PHASE 2: Trích xuất Embedding từ PhoBERT đã Fine-tuned\n", "## 5. PHASE 2: Trích xuất Embedding từ PhoBERT đã Fine-tuned\n", "## 5. PHASE 2: Trích xuất Embedding từ PhoBERT đã Fine-tuned\n", "Sử dụng PhoBERT đã fine-tuned để trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] 768 chiều cho mỗi review.", "Sử dụng PhoBERT đã fine-tuned để trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] 768 chiều cho mỗi review.", "Sử dụng PhoBERT đã fine-tuned để trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] 768 chiều cho mỗi review.", "Sử dụng PhoBERT đã fine-tuned để trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] 768 chiều cho mỗi review.", "Sử dụng PhoBERT đã fine-tuned để trích xuất tôibedding [CLS] 768 chiều cho mỗi review."]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 14, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 391}, "id": "yDFwYHbGwTAz", "outputId": "559bd787-22f9-4070-ee75-bce4b9033507"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["🔄 Trích xuất Fine-tuned embeddings...\n", "  📊 Train set...\n", "    Batch 50/448\n", "    Batch 100/448\n", "    Batch 150/448\n", "    Batch 200/448\n", "    Batch 250/448\n", "    Batch 300/448\n", "    Batch 350/448\n", "    Batch 400/448\n", "  📊 Dev set...\n", "    Batch 50/50\n", "  📊 Test set...\n", "    Batch 50/125\n", "    Batch 100/125\n", "\n", "✅ Fine-tuned embeddings: (14306, 768)\n", "   Train: (14306, 768), Dev: (1590, 768), Test: (3974, 768)\n"]}], "source": ["def extract_finetuned_tôibeddings(model, dataloader, device):\n", "    \"\"\"Trích xuất [CLS] tôibedding từ PhoBERT đã fine-tuned.\"\"\"\n", "    model.eval()\n", "    all_tôibeddings = []\n", "\n", "    with torch.no_grad():\n", "        for i, batch in enumerate(dataloader):\n", "            input_ids = batch['input_ids'].to(device)\n", "            attention_mask = batch['attention_mask'].to(device)\n", "\n", "            tôibeddings = model.extract_tôibeddings(input_ids, attention_mask)\n", "            all_tôibeddings.append(tôibeddings.cpu().numpy())\n", "\n", "            if (i + 1) % 50 == 0:\n", "                print(f'    Batch {i+1}/{len(dataloader)}')\n", "\n", "    return np.vstack(all_tôibeddings)\n", "\n", "print('🔄 Trích xuất Fine-tuned tôibeddings...')\n", "\n", "# Dataloader không shuffle để giữ thứ tự\n", "train_loader_noshuffle = DataLoader(train_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_EXTRACT, shuffle=False)\n", "dev_loader_extract = DataLoader(dev_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_EXTRACT, shuffle=False)\n", "test_loader_extract = DataLoader(test_dataset, batch_size=BATCH_SIZE_EXTRACT, shuffle=False)\n", "\n", "print('  📊 Train set...')\n", "X_ft_train = extract_finetuned_tôibeddings(model, train_loader_noshuffle, device)\n", "print('  📊 Dev set...')\n", "X_ft_dev = extract_finetuned_tôibeddings(model, dev_loader_extract, device)\n", "print('  📊 Test set...')\n", "X_ft_test = extract_finetuned_tôibeddings(model, test_loader_extract, device)\n", "\n", "print(f'\\n✅ Fine-tuned tôibeddings: {X_ft_train.shape}')\n", "print(f'   Train: {X_ft_train.shape}, Dev: {X_ft_dev.shape}, Test: {X_ft_test.shape}')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 15, "metadata": {"id": "_88DgxN-wTAz"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["✅ Combined features: 780 chiều\n", "   = 768 (fine-tuned PhoBERT) + 12 (handcrafted)\n", "🧹 GPU memory freed!\n"]}], "source": ["# Kết hợp Fine-tuned tôibedding + Handcrafted features\n", "X_combined_train = np.hstack([X_ft_train, X_hc_train])\n", "X_combined_dev = np.hstack([X_ft_dev, X_hc_dev])\n", "X_combined_test = np.hstack([X_ft_test, X_hc_test])\n", "\n", "print(f'✅ Combined features: {X_combined_train.shape[1]} chiều')\n", "print(f'   = {X_ft_train.shape[1]} (fine-tuned PhoBERT) + {X_hc_train.shape[1]} (handcrafted)')\n", "\n", "# Free GPU mtôiory (không cần PhoBERT nữa)\n", "del model\n", "gc.collect()\n", "torch.cuda.tôipty_cache()\n", "print('🧹 GPU mtôiory freed!')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "Wc64PjKUwTAz"}, "source": ["## 6. PHASE 3: Huấn luyện XGBoost trên Fine-tuned Embeddings\n", "## 6. PHASE 3: Huấn luyện XGBoost trên Fine-tuned Embeddings\n", "## 6. PHASE 3: Huấn luyện XGBoost trên Fine-tuned Embeddings\n", "## 6. PHASE 3: Huấn luyện XGBoost trên Fine-tuned Embeddings\n", "## 6. PHASE 3: Huấn luyện XGBoost trên Fine-tuned Embeddings\n", "Tối ưu siêu tham số bằng Optuna, rồi đánh giá trên tập test.", "Tối ưu siêu tham số bằng Optuna, rồi đánh giá trên tập test.", "Tối ưu siêu tham số bằng Optuna, rồi đánh giá trên tập test.", "Tối ưu siêu tham số bằng Optuna, rồi đánh giá trên tập test.", "Tối ưu siêu tham số bằng Optuna, rồi đánh giá trên tập test."]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 16, "metadata": {"id": "ZBW85XZYwTAz"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["============================================================\n", "🚀 PHASE 3: Optuna Hyperparameter Tuning cho XGBoost\n", "============================================================\n"]}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "2886654d4f1644309b411e3aa88372fa", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["  0%|          | 0/60 [00:00<?, ?it/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["\n", "✅ Best F1-macro (dev): 0.8886\n", "📋 Best params:\n", "   n_estimators: 549\n", "   max_depth: 9\n", "   learning_rate: 0.044598751168482394\n", "   subsample: 0.8952332502540541\n", "   colsample_bytree: 0.43555821452627863\n", "   min_child_weight: 10\n", "   gamma: 3.4033968738879974\n", "   reg_alpha: 0.3682434799589797\n", "   reg_lambda: 1.215705707100175\n", "CPU times: user 1h 1min 45s, sys: 19.5 s, total: 1h 2min 4s\n", "Wall time: 1h 2min 23s\n"]}], "source": ["%%time\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print('🚀 PHASE 3: Optuna Hyperparameter Tuning cho XGBoost')\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "\n", "scale_pos = n_real / n_spam\n", "\n", "def objective(trial):\n", "    params = {\n", "        'n_estimators': trial.suggest_int('n_estimators', 100, 600),\n", "        'max_depth': trial.suggest_int('max_depth', 3, 10),\n", "        'learning_rate': trial.suggest_float('learning_rate', 0.01, 0.3, log=True),\n", "        'subsample': trial.suggest_float('subsample', 0.6, 1.0),\n", "        'colsample_bytree': trial.suggest_float('colsample_bytree', 0.3, 0.8),\n", "        'min_child_weight': trial.suggest_int('min_child_weight', 1, 10),\n", "        'gamma': trial.suggest_float('gamma', 0.0, 5.0),\n", "        'reg_alpha': trial.suggest_float('reg_alpha', 0.0, 1.0),\n", "        'reg_lambda': trial.suggest_float('reg_lambda', 0.0, 5.0),\n", "        'scale_pos_weight': scale_pos,\n", "        'eval_metric': 'logloss',\n", "        'use_label_encoder': False,\n", "        'random_state': 42,\n", "        'n_jobs': -1,\n", "        'tree_method': 'hist',\n", "    }\n", "\n", "    clf = xgb.XGBClassifier(**params)\n", "    clf.fit(\n", "        X_combined_train, y_train,\n", "        eval_set=[(X_combined_dev, y_dev)],\n", "        verbose=False\n", "    )\n", "\n", "    dev_preds = clf.predict(X_combined_dev)\n", "    return f1_score(y_dev, dev_preds, average='macro')\n", "\n", "study = optuna.create_study(direction='maximize', study_name='FT_XGBoost')\n", "study.optimize(objective, n_trials=OPTUNA_TRIALS, show_progress_bar=True)\n", "\n", "print(f'\\n✅ Best F1-macro (dev): {study.best_value:.4f}')\n", "print(f'📋 Best params:')\n", "for k, v in study.best_params.ittôis():\n", "    print(f'   {k}: {v}')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 20, "metadata": {"id": "JlEovIZgwTA0"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["🏋️ Training final model với best params...\n", "💾 Saved XGBoost model: /content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib\n", "\n", "✅ Final model trained and evaluated!\n"]}], "source": ["# Train final model với best params\n", "import joblib\n", "\n", "print('🏋️ Training final model với best params...')\n", "best_params = study.best_params\n", "best_params.update({\n", "    'scale_pos_weight': scale_pos,\n", "    'eval_metric': 'logloss',\n", "    'use_label_encoder': False,\n", "    'random_state': 42,\n", "    'n_jobs': -1,\n", "    'tree_method': 'hist',\n", "})\n", "\n", "best_model = xgb.XGBClassifier(**best_params)\n", "best_model.fit(\n", "    X_combined_train, y_train,\n", "    eval_set=[(X_combined_dev, y_dev)],\n", "    verbose=False\n", ")\n", "\n", "# Save XGBoost model for inference API\n", "xgb_ckpt_path = f'{MODEL_PATH}/best_xgb.joblib'\n", "joblib.dump(best_model, xgb_ckpt_path)\n", "print(f'💾 Saved XGBoost model: {xgb_ckpt_path}')\n", "\n", "# Predict trên test set\n", "test_preds = best_model.predict(X_combined_test)\n", "test_probs = best_model.predict_proba(X_combined_test)[:, 1]\n", "\n", "print('\\n✅ Final model trained and evaluated!')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "poqAOQJTwTA0"}, "source": ["## 7. Đánh giá kết quả", "## 7. Đánh giá kết quả", "## 7. Đánh giá kết quả", "## 7. Đánh giá kết quả", "## 7. Đánh giá kết quả"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 21, "metadata": {"id": "Oy8j_lYGwTA0"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["============================================================\n", "📊 KẾT QUẢ: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Ensemble)\n", "============================================================\n", "  Accuracy:        0.9104 (91.04%)\n", "  Precision (macro): 0.8878\n", "  Recall (macro):    0.8899\n", "  F1-score (macro):  0.8889\n", "  F1-score (weighted): 0.9105\n", "  AUC-ROC:           0.9612\n", "\n", "📋 Classification Report:\n", "              precision    recall  f1-score   support\n", "\n", "        Real       0.94      0.94      0.94      2867\n", "        Spam       0.84      0.84      0.84      1107\n", "\n", "    accuracy                           0.91      3974\n", "   macro avg       0.89      0.89      0.89      3974\n", "weighted avg       0.91      0.91      0.91      3974\n", "\n", "\n", "💾 Results saved to /content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/results/results_ft_xgboost.json\n"]}], "source": ["# === ĐÁNH GIÁ ===\n", "acc = accuracy_score(y_test, test_preds)\n", "prec_macro = precision_score(y_test, test_preds, average='macro')\n", "rec_macro = recall_score(y_test, test_preds, average='macro')\n", "f1_macro = f1_score(y_test, test_preds, average='macro')\n", "f1_weighted = f1_score(y_test, test_preds, average='weighted')\n", "auc = roc_auc_score(y_test, test_probs)\n", "\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print('📊 KẾT QUẢ: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible)')\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print(f'  Accuracy:        {acc:.4f} ({acc*100:.2f}%)')\n", "print(f'  Precision (macro): {prec_macro:.4f}')\n", "print(f'  Recall (macro):    {rec_macro:.4f}')\n", "print(f'  F1-score (macro):  {f1_macro:.4f}')\n", "print(f'  F1-score (weighted): {f1_weighted:.4f}')\n", "print(f'  AUC-ROC:           {auc:.4f}')\n", "print('\\n📋 Classification Report:')\n", "print(classification_report(y_test, test_preds, target_names=['Real', 'Spam']))\n", "\n", "# Lưu kết quả\n", "results = {\n", "    'PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost': {\n", "        'accuracy': acc,\n", "        'precision_macro': prec_macro,\n", "        'recall_macro': rec_macro,\n", "        'f1_macro': f1_macro,\n", "        'f1_weighted': f1_weighted,\n", "        'auc_roc': auc,\n", "        'best_params': study.best_params,\n", "    }\n", "}\n", "\n", "with open(f'{RESULT_PATH}/results_ft_xgboost.json', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n", "    json.dump(results, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False, default=str)\n", "print(f'\\n💾 Results saved to {RESULT_PATH}/results_ft_xgboost.json')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "vcIyNN-ewTA0"}, "source": ["## 8. So sánh tất cả phương pháp", "## 8. So sánh tất cả phương pháp", "## 8. So sánh tất cả phương pháp", "## 8. So sánh tất cả phương pháp", "## 8. So sánh tất cả phương pháp"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 22, "metadata": {"id": "WZBRk8HewTA0"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["\n", "📊 SO SÁNH TẤT CẢ PHƯƠNG PHÁP:\n", "======================================================================\n", "                                 Accuracy  F1-macro   AUC-ROC\n", "XGBoost + Handcrafted            0.825600  0.771000  0.810300\n", "XGBoost + PhoBERT (frozen)       0.854800  0.809700  0.898600\n", "XGBoost + Combined (frozen)      0.876400  0.835200  0.916300\n", "PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone)  0.909200  0.886300  0.957400\n", "⭐ Fine-tuned + XGBoost (NEW)     0.910418  0.888867  0.961237\n", "======================================================================\n", "\n", "🏆 Phương pháp tốt nhất (Accuracy): ⭐ Fine-tuned + XGBoost (NEW)\n", "🏆 Phương pháp tốt nhất (F1-macro): ⭐ Fine-tuned + XGBoost (NEW)\n"]}], "source": ["# So sánh với các phương pháp trước\n", "comparison = {\n", "    'XGBoost + Handcrafted': {'accuracy': 0.8256, 'f1_macro': 0.7710, 'auc_roc': 0.8103},\n", "    'XGBoost + PhoBERT (frozen)': {'accuracy': 0.8548, 'f1_macro': 0.8097, 'auc_roc': 0.8986},\n", "    'XGBoost + Combined (frozen)': {'accuracy': 0.8764, 'f1_macro': 0.8352, 'auc_roc': 0.9163},\n", "    'PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone)': {'accuracy': 0.9092, 'f1_macro': 0.8863, 'auc_roc': 0.9574},\n", "    '⭐ Fine-tuned + XGBoost (NEW)': {'accuracy': acc, 'f1_macro': f1_macro, 'auc_roc': auc},\n", "}\n", "\n", "df_compare = pd.DataFrame(comparison).T\n", "df_compare.columns = ['Accuracy', 'F1-macro', 'AUC-ROC']\n", "df_compare = df_compare.sort_values('Accuracy')\n", "\n", "print('\\n📊 SO SÁNH TẤT CẢ PHƯƠNG PHÁP:')\n", "print('=' * 70)\n", "print(df_compare.to_string())\n", "print('=' * 70)\n", "\n", "# Highlight kết quả\n", "best_method = df_compare['Accuracy'].idxmax()\n", "print(f'\\n🏆 Phương pháp tốt nhất (Accuracy): {best_method}')\n", "best_f1_method = df_compare['F1-macro'].idxmax()\n", "print(f'🏆 Phương pháp tốt nhất (F1-macro): {best_f1_method}')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 23, "metadata": {"id": "tyXrP5LDwTA0"}, "outputs": [{"data": {"image/png": "", "text/plain": ["<Figure size 1800x600 with 3 Axes>"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["💾 Chart saved!\n"]}], "source": ["# === VISUALIZATION ===\n", "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 6))\n", "\n", "colors = ['#94a3b8', '#94a3b8', '#6366f1', '#22c55e', '#ef4444']\n", "\n", "for idx, metric in enumerate(['Accuracy', 'F1-macro', 'AUC-ROC']):\n", "    ax = axes[idx]\n", "    vals = df_compare[metric]\n", "    bars = ax.barh(range(len(vals)), vals, color=colors)\n", "    ax.set_yticks(range(len(vals)))\n", "    ax.set_yticklabels(df_compare.index, fontsize=9)\n", "    ax.set_xlabel(metric)\n", "    ax.set_title(f'{metric} Comparison', fontweight='bold')\n", "\n", "    for bar, val in zip(bars, vals):\n", "        ax.text(val + 0.002, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2,\n", "                f'{val:.4f}', va='center', fontsize=9)\n", "\n", "plt.tight_layout()\n", "plt.savefig(f'{RESULT_PATH}/comparison_ft_xgboost.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n", "plt.show()\n", "print(f'💾 Chart saved!')"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 24, "metadata": {"id": "yPq-3oeRwTA0"}, "outputs": [{"data": {"image/png": "", "text/plain": ["<Figure size 800x600 with 2 Axes>"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}], "source": ["# === CONFUSION MATRIX ===\n", "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 6))\n", "cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, test_preds)\n", "sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues',\n", "            xticklabels=['Real', 'Spam'], yticklabels=['Real', 'Spam'], ax=ax)\n", "ax.set_xlabel('Predicted')\n", "ax.set_ylabel('Actual')\n", "ax.set_title('Confusion Matrix: PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost', fontweight='bold')\n", "plt.tight_layout()\n", "plt.savefig(f'{RESULT_PATH}/cm_ft_xgboost.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n", "plt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 25, "metadata": {"id": "PWxilU7KwTA0"}, "outputs": [{"data": {"image/png": "", "text/plain": ["<Figure size 1000x800 with 1 Axes>"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["\n", "📊 Trong top 20 features:\n", "   PhoBERT fine-tuned dims: 20\n", "   Handcrafted features:    0\n"]}], "source": ["# === FEATURE IMPORTANCE (top 20) ===\n", "feature_names = [f'phobert_ft_{i}' for i in range(EMBED_DIM)] + [\n", "    'text_length', 'word_count', 'avg_word_length', 'uppercase_ratio',\n", "    'exclamation_count', 'question_count', 'tôioji_count', 'is_short_review',\n", "    'is_long_review', 'digit_ratio', 'unique_word_ratio', 'newline_count'\n", "]\n", "\n", "importances = best_model.feature_importances_\n", "top_indices = np.argsort(importances)[-20:][::-1]\n", "\n", "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))\n", "top_names = [feature_names[i] for i in top_indices]\n", "top_vals = [importances[i] for i in top_indices]\n", "\n", "# Color: đỏ cho handcrafted, xanh cho PhoBERT\n", "bar_colors = ['#ef4444' if not n.startswith('phobert_ft_') else '#6366f1' for n in top_names]\n", "\n", "ax.barh(range(len(top_names)), top_vals, color=bar_colors)\n", "ax.set_yticks(range(len(top_names)))\n", "ax.set_yticklabels(top_names)\n", "ax.invert_yaxis()\n", "ax.set_xlabel('Feature Importance')\n", "ax.set_title('Top 20 Features: Fine-tuned PhoBERT + XGBoost', fontweight='bold')\n", "\n", "# Legend\n", "from matplotlib.patches import Patch\n", "legend_eltôients = [\n", "    Patch(facecolor='#6366f1', label='PhoBERT Fine-tuned Embedding'),\n", "    Patch(facecolor='#ef4444', label='Handcrafted Feature')\n", "]\n", "ax.legend(handles=legend_eltôients, loc='lower right')\n", "\n", "plt.tight_layout()\n", "plt.savefig(f'{RESULT_PATH}/feature_importance_ft_xgboost.png', dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n", "plt.show()\n", "\n", "# Thống kê\n", "hc_in_top20 = sum(1 for n in top_names if not n.startswith('phobert_ft_'))\n", "print(f'\\n📊 Trong top 20 features:')\n", "print(f'   PhoBERT fine-tuned dims: {20 - hc_in_top20}')\n", "print(f'   Handcrafted features:    {hc_in_top20}')"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "tOASQEe7wTA1"}, "source": ["## 9. Kết luận", "## 9. Kết luận", "## 9. Kết luận", "## 9. Kết luận", "## 9. Kết luận"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 26, "metadata": {"id": "wssIjNmdwTA1"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["\n", "============================================================\n", "📝 KẾT LUẬN THỰC NGHIỆM\n", "============================================================\n", "\n", "PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Ensemble):\n", "  Accuracy:  0.9104 (91.04%)\n", "  F1-macro:  0.8889\n", "  AUC-ROC:   0.9612\n", "\n", "So sánh:\n", "  vs XGBoost + Combined (frozen):     Acc +0.0340, F1 +0.0537\n", "  vs PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): Acc +0.0012, F1 +0.0026\n", "\n", "Giả thuyết kiểm chứng:\n", "  - Nếu kết quả > 90.92%: Ensemble tốt hơn, handcrafted features bổ sung giá trị\n", "  - Nếu kết quả ~ 87-90%: Embedding fine-tuned mạnh hơn frozen, nhưng\n", "    tách ra khỏi end-to-end pipeline làm mất thông tin\n", "  - Nếu kết quả < 87.64%: Có vấn đề trong pipeline, cần debug\n", "\n", "============================================================\n"]}], "source": ["print('\\n' + '=' * 60)\n", "print('📝 KẾT LUẬN THỰC NGHIỆM')\n", "print('=' * 60)\n", "print(f'''\n", "PhoBERT Fine-tuned + XGBoost (Enstôible):\n", "  Accuracy:  {acc:.4f} ({acc*100:.2f}%)\n", "  F1-macro:  {f1_macro:.4f}\n", "  AUC-ROC:   {auc:.4f}\n", "\n", "So sánh:\n", "  vs XGBoost + Combined (frozen):     Acc {acc-0.8764:+.4f}, F1 {f1_macro-0.8352:+.4f}\n", "  vs PhoBERT Fine-tuned (standalone): Acc {acc-0.9092:+.4f}, F1 {f1_macro-0.8863:+.4f}\n", "\n", "Giả thuyết kiểm chứng:\n", "  - Nếu kết quả > 90.92%: Enstôible tốt hơn, handcrafted features bổ sung giá trị\n", "  - Nếu kết quả ~ 87-90%: Embedding fine-tuned mạnh hơn frozen, nhưng\n", "    tách ra khỏi end-to-end pipeline làm mất thông tin\n", "  - Nếu kết quả < 87.64%: Có vấn đề trong pipeline, cần debug\n", "''')\n", "print('=' * 60)"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "BpagG5-xvcuI"}, "source": ["Tao API", "Tao API", "Tao API", "Tao API", "Tao API"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 6, "metadata": {"id": "CJvQy2CkvV9a"}, "outputs": [], "source": ["PHOBERT_CKPT = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/phobert_finetuned_best.pt\"\n", "XGB_CKPT = \"/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib\""]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 7, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/", "height": 211}, "id": "QtvN-D0Fvf_8", "outputId": "688863a9-1aef-47d4-8b20-96c983e6b8da"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Local tokenizer cache not found. Downloading from Hugging Face...\n"]}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "01e0b1a21ebd4c4f8dad3c0a50c714b6", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["config.json:   0%|          | 0.00/557 [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stderr", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Warning: You are sending unauthenticated requests to the HF Hub. Please set a HF_TOKEN to enable higher rate limits and faster downloads.\n", "WARNING:huggingface_hub.utils._http:Warning: You are sending unauthenticated requests to the HF Hub. Please set a HF_TOKEN to enable higher rate limits and faster downloads.\n"]}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "ded3c8c2ebb64cc5aae2e9cf2b88ee9d", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["vocab.txt: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "c99fc42169ec48d98265b457563ad3dd", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["bpe.codes: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "33c28cef89d348d1a1a4eb977235e2dc", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["tokenizer.json: 0.00B [00:00, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Local model cache not found. Downloading base model from Hugging Face...\n"]}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "55a7b78bb8d04d59a98cb21aec94bbc9", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["pytorch_model.bin:   0%|          | 0.00/543M [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "b8c91ffcf96942e3ada18fa901c8ceb8", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["Loading weights:   0%|          | 0/199 [00:00<?, ?it/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"data": {"application/vnd.jupyter.widget-view+json": {"model_id": "3a511a7c1e674f0eb8c0735b6035238a", "version_major": 2, "version_minor": 0}, "text/plain": ["model.safetensors:   0%|          | 0.00/543M [00:00<?, ?B/s]"]}, "metadata": {}, "output_type": "display_data"}, {"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Loaded base_model and best_xgb OK\n", "Missing keys: 0 | Unexpected keys: 0\n"]}], "source": ["import os, torch, joblib\n", "import numpy as np\n", "from transformers import AutoTokenizer, AutoModel, logging as hf_logging\n", "import xgboost as xgb\n", "\n", "hf_logging.set_verbosity_error()\n", "\n", "assert os.path.exists(PHOBERT_CKPT), f\"Missing: {PHOBERT_CKPT}\"\n", "\n", "# If checkpoint file is missing but best_model exists in-mtôiory, save it automatically\n", "if not os.path.exists(XGB_CKPT):\n", "    if 'best_model' in globals():\n", "        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(XGB_CKPT), exist_ok=True)\n", "        joblib.dump(best_model, XGB_CKPT)\n", "        print(f\"⚠️ XGB checkpoint missing. Auto-saved from in-mtôiory best_model -> {XGB_CKPT}\")\n", "    else:\n", "        raise AssertionError(\n", "            f\"Missing: {XGB_CKPT}. Please run training cell (Phase 3) first to create best_model/joblib.\"\n", "        )\n", "\n", "device = \"cuda\" if torch.cuda.is_available() else \"cpu\"\n", "model_name = globals().get(\"PHOBERT_MODEL\", \"vinai/phobert-base\")\n", "\n", "# Reuse tokenizer/model from current kernel if available; otherwise prefer local cache first.\n", "if 'tokenizer' in globals():\n", "    print(\"Using tokenizer from current kernel...\")\n", "else:\n", "    try:\n", "        tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(model_name, local_files_only=True)\n", "        print(\"Loaded tokenizer from local cache.\")\n", "    except Exception:\n", "        print(\"Local tokenizer cache not found. Downloading from Hugging Face...\")\n", "        tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(model_name)\n", "\n", "# Load fine-tuned PhoBERT weights into AutoModel by stripping 'phobert.' prefix if needed\n", "try:\n", "    base_model = AutoModel.from_pretrained(model_name, local_files_only=True)\n", "    print(\"Loaded base model from local cache.\")\n", "except Exception:\n", "    print(\"Local model cache not found. Downloading base model from Hugging Face...\")\n", "    base_model = AutoModel.from_pretrained(model_name)\n", "\n", "raw_state = torch.load(PHOBERT_CKPT, map_location=device)\n", "if isinstance(raw_state, dict) and any(k.startswith('phobert.') for k in raw_state.keys()):\n", "    state = {k.replace('phobert.', '', 1): v for k, v in raw_state.ittôis() if k.startswith('phobert.')}\n", "else:\n", "    state = raw_state\n", "missing, unexpected = base_model.load_state_dict(state, strict=False)\n", "base_model.to(device)\n", "base_model.eval()\n", "\n", "best_xgb = joblib.load(XGB_CKPT)\n", "print(\"Loaded base_model and best_xgb OK\")\n", "print(f\"Missing keys: {len(missing)} | Unexpected keys: {len(unexpected)}\")"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 29, "metadata": {"colab": {"base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"}, "id": "zzNMNt03vt6O", "outputId": "42236cb7-868a-4f45-d39a-37bc4c411fca"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["Found: 2\n", "/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/models/best_xgb.joblib\n", "/content/drive/MyDrive/ViSpamDetection/results/results_ft_xgboost.json\n"]}], "source": ["import os, glob\n", "\n", "candidates = []\n", "for pattern in [\n", "    \"/content/drive/MyDrive/**/*.joblib\",\n", "    \"/content/drive/MyDrive/**/*.pkl\",\n", "    \"/content/drive/MyDrive/**/*.json\",\n", "]:\n", "    candidates += glob.glob(pattern, recursive=True)\n", "\n", "xgb_like = [p for p in candidates if any(k in p.lower() for k in [\"xgb\", \"xgboost\", \"best_model\"])]\n", "print(\"Found:\", len(xgb_like))\n", "for p in xgb_like[:200]:\n", "    print(p)"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": 8, "metadata": {"id": "pUn0qisxMnis"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stdout", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["URL của bạn là: NgrokTunnel: \"https://paleaceous-nonseclusively-dinah.ngrok-free.dev\" -> \"http://127.0.0.1:8000\"\n", "Forwarding to http://127.0.0.1:8000\n"]}], "source": ["from pyngrok import ngrok\n", "import os\n", "\n", "# Kill old tunnels\n", "ngrok.kill()\n", "\n", "# Hard-code ngrok auth token\n", "token = '3Aq0WZgXwq9wBkdxeFqjb4HbvFe_3nmu2nQ6JoeQYP6WVbqo6'.strip()\n", "if token:\n", "    ngrok.set_auth_token(token)\n", "else:\n", "    print('⚠️ Ngrok token is tôipty.')\n", "\n", "try:\n", "    public_url = ngrok.connect(addr='127.0.0.1:8000', proto='http', bind_tls=True)\n", "    print(f\"URL của bạn là: {public_url}\")\n", "    print('Forwarding to http://127.0.0.1:8000')\n", "except Exception as e:\n", "    print(f\"Lỗi: {e}\")"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {"id": "flHnVTj2PBPD"}, "outputs": [{"name": "stderr", "output_type": "stream", "text": ["INFO:     Started server process [847]\n", "INFO:     Waiting for 